565
00:41:56,350 --> 00:41:57,180
Okay.

566
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:04,480
Yeon-Joo.

567
00:42:05,850 --> 00:42:07,080
See you later tonight.

568
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:09,490
Promise?

569
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:14,090
Man, that was close.

