639
00:55:59,650 --> 00:56:01,990
Did you see anybody suspicious?

640
00:56:02,060 --> 00:56:03,990
Think about it.

641
00:56:04,060 --> 00:56:06,580
A man moves into a house with two girls...

642
00:56:06,660 --> 00:56:07,790
