643
00:56:10,160 --> 00:56:11,600
- Goodnight!
- You, too.

644
00:56:24,750 --> 00:56:27,080
Hyeong-Gook Park

645
00:56:34,520 --> 00:56:36,180
Hyeong-Gook Park, author

646
00:56:37,760 --> 00:56:38,890
No search result

647
00:56:46,130 --> 00:56:49,400
Mr. President.
What are you trying to do here?

648
00:56:50,270 --> 00:56:55,680
Our people underestimated it
because it was a residential house.

649
00:56:57,040 --> 00:56:58,880
I apologize.

650
00:57:10,760 --> 00:57:12,780
Stay out of grown-up business and

651
00:57:12,860 --> 00:57:17,190
go play with your friends,
okay midget?

652
00:57:21,570 --> 00:57:23,900
Mr. President.

653
00:57:23,970 --> 00:57:26,800
Do you think I don't know how to handle a girl?

654
00:57:26,870 --> 00:57:30,470
