655
00:57:30,550 --> 00:57:34,570
If any one of them talks,
your name will come up.

656
00:57:36,650 --> 00:57:40,090
A rich kid hires thugs to steal a piece of china...

657
00:57:40,150 --> 00:57:42,490
Your dad will be proud.

658
00:57:42,560 --> 00:57:46,490
Mr. Ghang.
Think of Mr. Ha's position.

659
00:57:46,560 --> 00:57:47,790
