660
00:57:48,960 --> 00:57:54,400
Mr. President.
Do you really want the Blue Dragon Tea Cup?

661
00:57:54,470 --> 00:57:59,000
Yes, of course.
Mr. Ghang, I want it.

662
00:57:59,070 --> 00:58:02,770
Then if you'd just let me be as I asked,

663
00:58:02,840 --> 00:58:07,180
it will all be resolved soon.

664
00:58:07,250 --> 00:58:10,380
Why are you being uncooperative?

665
00:58:10,450 --> 00:58:15,580
If this is what you want,
let's call the whole thing off.

666
00:58:17,190 --> 00:58:18,590
Don't be like that now,
Mr. Ghang.

667
00:58:18,660 --> 00:58:23,190
Just hang in there, okay?
Keep it up.

668
00:58:23,260 --> 00:58:27,790
Mr. Ghang.
Let's go now, okay?

669
00:58:37,040 --> 00:58:41,070
He's the one not keeping his word,
isn't he?

670
00:58:41,150 --> 00:58:44,980
I can understand where Mr. Ghang is coming from.

671
00:58:45,050 --> 00:58:46,880
Whose side are you on?

672
00:58:46,950 --> 00:58:48,080
I'm not siding with him.
It's just...

673
00:58:49,120 --> 00:58:51,490
If things go wrong,

674
00:58:51,560 --> 00:58:52,490
it won't be good for the company

675
00:58:52,560 --> 00:58:56,190
