Man, you're frigid!

676
00:58:57,060 --> 00:58:59,900
You should lay low until this gig is over.

677
00:59:00,770 --> 00:59:01,700
What's this?

678
00:59:01,870 --> 00:59:03,600
Chang-In Ghang

679
00:59:03,670 --> 00:59:06,700
A few years ago,
you did some work with Mr. Kwon?

680
00:59:06,770 --> 00:59:09,170
That was ages ago.

681
00:59:09,240 --> 00:59:10,680
