683
00:59:14,350 --> 00:59:16,870
Dumbasses.

684
00:59:16,950 --> 00:59:19,980
You keep stalling,
you'll be caught too.

685
00:59:20,050 --> 00:59:24,510
I was planning on leaving the
country after this gig anyway.

686
00:59:24,590 --> 00:59:26,820
You know the kid from back when

