695
01:00:47,640 --> 01:00:48,870
You know why.

696
01:00:52,250 --> 01:00:53,980
To be with me?

697
01:01:00,090 --> 01:01:02,580
You should go to work.

698
01:01:03,990 --> 01:01:08,590
Modern women are beautiful when they're at work.

699
01:01:11,700 --> 01:01:14,600
Come here.
I'll tuck you in.

700
01:01:19,710 --> 01:01:22,010
And you'll go to work tomorrow.

701
01:01:22,080 --> 01:01:23,700
Okay.

702
01:01:26,450 --> 01:01:29,680
Alarm disabled.
Welcome.

703
01:01:57,040 --> 01:01:59,670
Shouldn't you be in school?

704
01:02:02,450 --> 01:02:06,280
Well, how do I say this?

705
01:02:07,560 --> 01:02:10,990
When I was your age,

706
01:02:11,060 --> 01:02:14,690
I didn't want to go to school either.

707
01:02:14,760 --> 01:02:17,600
You can stay there,
you know.

708
01:02:17,670 --> 01:02:20,400
There were some difficult times.

709
01:02:21,970 --> 01:02:22,800
Wait!

710
01:02:29,240 --> 01:02:32,270
- Yeon-Joo.
- Hi, sir.

711
01:02:34,650 --> 01:02:36,980
Your daughter is home.

712
01:02:38,750 --> 01:02:39,780
So?

713
01:02:39,850 --> 01:02:43,980
Shouldn't she be in school at this hour?

714
01:02:44,060 --> 01:02:45,990
Pay no attention.

715
01:02:46,630 --> 01:02:49,390
