considered child endangerment.

719
01:02:58,210 --> 01:02:59,430
Watch yourself!

720
01:02:59,510 --> 01:03:04,100
No, as a member of UNICEF,
I must say something.

721
01:03:04,180 --> 01:03:05,410
Send her to school.

722
01:03:05,480 --> 01:03:07,880
That's the right thing to do as a parent.

723
01:03:10,890 --> 01:03:13,320
Why did you skip school again?
You made me look bad.

724
01:03:13,390 --> 01:03:14,220
What's going on with you lately?

725
01:03:14,290 --> 01:03:16,020
Since when do you care about my school?

726
01:03:16,090 --> 01:03:17,610
When have I not cared?

727
01:03:17,690 --> 01:03:21,220
