to the school every morning?

728
01:03:21,300 --> 01:03:23,820
You wanted to practice driving.

729
01:03:23,900 --> 01:03:25,130
What's gotten into you today?

730
01:03:25,200 --> 01:03:26,430
Don't even think about getting your face fixed.

731
01:03:26,500 --> 01:03:28,090
Fix your personality first!

732
01:03:28,600 --> 01:03:32,770
My face can be fixed,
but not my personality.

733
01:03:32,840 --> 01:03:34,710
Because I was born mean.

734
01:03:34,780 --> 01:03:36,000
Mom, you've got it better though.

735
01:03:36,080 --> 01:03:37,810
You're pretty even with bad personality.

736
01:03:37,880 --> 01:03:39,210
What a thing to say to her mother!?

737
01:03:39,280 --> 01:03:40,510
Seriously, what's wrong with you?

738
01:03:40,580 --> 01:03:42,910
