Why start being a mom now?

739
01:03:42,980 --> 01:03:44,920
Some mothers toss their kids off the balcony,

740
01:03:44,990 --> 01:03:46,580
Because they don't want to raise them.

741
01:03:46,650 --> 01:03:48,590
You should be thankful.

742
01:03:48,660 --> 01:03:50,590
And she calls herself a mom.

743
01:04:09,700 --> 01:04:12,230
I was only nineteen years old.

744
01:04:12,710 --> 01:04:14,540
