753
01:04:36,530 --> 01:04:37,660
She was pretty like me when she was little.

754
01:04:37,730 --> 01:04:39,260
She's still pretty,
just as long as she doesn't skip school...

755
01:04:39,330 --> 01:04:41,730
Yeah, she's pretty.

756
01:04:41,800 --> 01:04:43,330
She's okay,
but her personality is not pretty.

757
01:04:46,110 --> 01:04:48,870
Whenever I saw her father's face in her,

758
01:04:48,940 --> 01:04:49,810
I just...

759
01:04:53,210 --> 01:04:55,650
Full of stupid hopes to run a big business,

760
01:04:55,720 --> 01:04:57,740
investing in all kinds of failure

761
01:04:58,220 --> 01:04:59,950
All he left me is just the tiny store.

762
01:05:00,620 --> 01:05:01,650
