763
01:05:05,030 --> 01:05:06,860
Yeon-Joo, calm down.

764
01:05:08,330 --> 01:05:09,760
Just focus on Seong-Ah.

765
01:05:09,830 --> 01:05:12,060
We should've bought an apartment building,
like I said.

766
01:05:12,500 --> 01:05:13,930
A house with a yard.
A yard?

767
01:05:14,000 --> 01:05:14,870
When he was obsessed with getting a yard,

768
01:05:14,940 --> 01:05:16,230
I should have stopped him,

769
01:05:16,900 --> 01:05:19,530
