773
01:05:30,950 --> 01:05:33,750
Isn't the gallery spending not open to public?

774
01:05:33,820 --> 01:05:37,050
Your father gave the order.

775
01:05:38,930 --> 01:05:39,950
Dad?

776
01:05:41,600 --> 01:05:44,660
